title: Easy Tex-Mex Chicken & Onion Chutney Glaze with Roast Veggie Toss
description: Eat the sunset with this glowing veggie toss, roasted to crisp perfection and tossed with charred corn. Tex-Mex
spices on chicken continue those rich colours and flavours, dig in and enjoy feeling as warm as a sunset!

